Description of the table C_PIB_SVMXC_INSTALLED_PRODUCT_BUSINESS_PARTNER

20-Nov-2022

 

All devices/equipment from ServiceMax Installed Product table. Business Partners fields on the Devie record are normalized to an individual row.

PARTNER_FUNCTION =

Account

Location Account (the Account of the Location partner is stored)

 

Note: the Location partner is available on PIB_SVMXC_DEVICE

 

Source: SVMXC__Installed_Product__c, no filters

 

Filter: none, deleted rows are included with IS_DELETED = Y

 

Update Frequency: daily changes to SystemModStamp
